  "description": [
    "Students who have taken more than one year of Latin in high school, but have not yet taken a Latin course at Fitchburg State University, are required to take a placement exam if they wish to register for a Latin course at the university level. Based on the results of the test, the student and instructor will determine the appropriate level of class for the student."
